A warm, sunlit hawker center scene in Singapore rendered in Studio Ghibli style, two empty chairs facing each other at a small round table covered with half-finished plates of local food and steaming cups of kopi, afternoon light streaming through the open-air architecture casting soft golden shadows, tropical plants visible in the background, a sense of connection and pleasant conversation lingering in the air despite the absent figures, warm ochre and jade green color palette, gentle brushwork capturing the humid tropical atmosphere.
